# Cursor Rule — Voucher Project Overview

This is an online discount voucher e-commerce final project.

Use JavaScript, not TypeScript.
Use React 18 + Vite frontend and Express backend.
Use PostgreSQL + Prisma, not MongoDB.

Core flow:
Partner creates voucher -> Admin approves -> Customer buys -> Mock payment -> Issue unique voucher code -> Partner redeems -> Reports/audit logs.

Do not implement real payment, SMS, email, microservices, or MongoDB.
